Package: sequenceRCT
Type: Package
Title: Sequence Analysis Tools for Randomized Controlled Trials
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Jane", "Doe",
      email = "jane@example.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides agnostic functions to simulate, analyze, and visualize behavioral sequences
    from randomized controlled trials. Includes tools for Markov-based sequence simulation,
    empirical transition estimation, complexity metrics (entropy, turbulence, volatility),
    hierarchical clustering, and alluvial transition diagrams.
License: GPL-3
